snippet.title: Saraswati Mantra | Om Saraswati Namo Namah | Basant Panchami | Saraswati Puja | Master Your Mind
snippet.description:
Experience the divine power of the Saraswati Mantra, a sacred Vedic chant dedicated to Goddess Saraswati‚Äîthe eternal source of wisdom, intelligence, creativity, and clarity of thought. This mantra is traditionally known to enhance learning, focus, communication skills, and decision-making abilities, which are essential foundations for achieving success in modern life, including career growth, financial planning, and wealth creation.

In today‚Äôs fast-paced world of technology, luxury lifestyle, high-performance careers, and global financial markets, mental clarity and disciplined thinking are more valuable than ever. Regular listening to the Saraswati Mantra helps calm the mind, sharpen analytical skills, and align your thoughts toward positive outcomes. A focused mind is crucial for excelling in investment strategies, stock market analysis, business leadership, entrepreneurship, and long-term financial stability.

Many successful individuals across the world believe that spiritual discipline complements material growth. When your mind is balanced, you make wiser choices‚Äîwhether it‚Äôs related to personal finance, wealth management, real estate investment, or building assets that support a premium lifestyle. Listening to this mantra during meditation, work, or study can support better concentration, improved productivity, and confident communication‚Äîskills valued in corporate careers, high-income professions, and global businesses.

This devotional audio is ideal for those aspiring to grow in financial wealth, career success, and intellectual excellence, while remaining spiritually grounded. It resonates strongly with audiences interested in luxury cars, automobiles, high-end brands, financial freedom, passive income, and smart money habits. A calm and intelligent mindset also supports better judgment when dealing with banking, insurance, mutual funds, cryptocurrency awareness, and international investments.

Listening to the Saraswati Mantra daily can inspire discipline, creativity, and confidence‚Äîqualities that align naturally with success in business growth, startup ecosystems, digital marketing, global employment opportunities, and lifestyle goals. Whether you are a student, professional, entrepreneur, or investor, this mantra helps cultivate inner strength that supports both spiritual peace and material progress.

üå∏ Listen with devotion
üå∏ Chant along or play during work or meditation
üå∏ Maintain a positive intention for knowledge, growth, and prosperity

May Goddess Saraswati bless you with wisdom that leads to meaningful success, balanced wealth, and a fulfilled life

Singer, Music Director & Lyrics :- Sohini Mishra
Video :- Mindpro Agency

Lyrics: 
Lu hai Manungkotaima mero dil basyo lali othaimaa.
Lu hai manung kotaima najar nalagau lali othaima.

Pirati lam na ta Saili ghumna lai jamna ta.
Pirati launna ma Saila ekdine pauna sa.

Oi hoi damauli katesi madiko pool hitaiko mayalai gulab ko phool.

Ghara mero rukumai timi Mam pareu ukhumai.
Ghar mero tanahu ho launa ke bhanam bhanam bho.

Na rup maa khot timro sundar gulabi otha timro.
Ke hereu tesari o kho laaj lagyo besari.

O hoi marsyandi salala paniko bhel kisimai raichha ni mayako khel.

Tan ramro Mam ramro timi lajauda jhan ramro.
Jiu pani kasilo timro muharai hasilo.

Ke socheu bhanata timle paraichheu Manata.
Ma ta gurung ki chhori ho mero khyalmai dil chori bho.

snippet.title: VEK X Oshin Karki - Pari Katha (Prod. by SNJV ) (ClassX Rush Live Track 2)
snippet.description:
ClassX Rush - Live Track No. 2 

From hearing her voice on an Instagram Live to finally creating together this truly feels like a dream come true.

In this episode of ClassX RUSH - LIVE, watch and listen as Oshin and I craft a complete track from scratch in just 3 hours and 13 minutes. From the first idea to writing every word, shaping melodies, and building the final sound.

This session captures the beauty of spontaneous creativity, collaboration, and trusting the process.
I want to extend a huge thank you to our extremely talented producers, SNJV and POZOD, who played a major role in creating this masterpiece.
Much love as well to my brothers KEEMA , NIXDII and SAGE for the incredible company and energy throughout the session. ü§ç

ClassX RUSH - LIVE is a space where ideas turn into music and artists come together to create without boundaries. This is only the beginning many more exciting artists will be joining this journey very soon.

snippet.description:
Experience a fresh take on the timeless Nepali folk classic, "Allare Nani Kesi." Originally composed and sung by the legendary Jhalakman Gandharva, this remake version is beautifully reimagined by Yubaraj Portel only on Music Nepal's Official YouTube Channel.

This version brings modern production while keeping the soulful essence of the Sarangi and the traditional Gandharva roots alive for a new generation.

"‡§Ö‡§≤‡•ç‡§≤‡§æ‡§∞‡•á ‡§®‡§æ‡§®‡•Ä" (Allare Nani Kesi) ‡§è‡§â‡§ü‡§æ ‡§ï‡§æ‡§≤‡§ú‡§Ø‡•Ä ‡§®‡•á‡§™‡§æ‡§≤‡•Ä ‡§≤‡•ã‡§ï ‡§ó‡•Ä‡§§ ‡§π‡•ã‡•§  ‡§Ø‡•Å‡§µ‡§∞‡§æ‡§ú ‡§™‡•ã‡§∞‡•ç‡§ü‡•á‡§≤‡§ï‡•ã ‡§∞‡§ø‡§Æ‡•á‡§ï ‡§∏‡§Ç‡§∏‡•ç‡§ï‡§∞‡§£ ‡§∞ ‡§ù‡§≤‡§ï‡§Æ‡§æ‡§® ‡§ó‡§®‡•ç‡§ß‡§∞‡•ç‡§µ‡§ï‡•ã ‡§Æ‡•å‡§≤‡§ø‡§ï (Original) ‡§∏‡§Ç‡§∏‡•ç‡§ï‡§∞‡§£‡§Æ‡§æ,

This folk melody reflects the culture, tradition, and heartfelt emotions of Nepali villages. A perfect combination of soulful lyrics, traditional instruments, and rhythmic beats.
Enjoy the real taste of Nepali Lok Geet Dohori and regional music heritage. Celebrate the spirit of Nepal through Music Nepal‚Äôs timeless Lok Geet collection, bringing together authentic Nepali folk sounds. Experience soulful traditional music with rich melodies and heartfelt folk emotions.  A beautiful blend of lok dohori and classic traditional rhythms that portray love, devotion, culture, and village life.

snippet.title: YABI - AJAVOLI ft. BLUESSS ( OFFICIAL AUDIO )
snippet.description:
Track 2 from the BOOMERANG mixtape, ‚ÄúAjavoli‚Äù featuring Bluesss, delivers smooth melodies and emotional storytelling. A song about love, reflection, and feelings that never fade, this track shows a softer but powerful side of Yabi The Goat.


Heartfelt thanks to RACHANA DAHAL  for the beautiful back vocals. Your voice added depth, emotion, and soul to this track. Truly grateful for your support and talent.

‚ÄòAjavoli‚Äô is inspired by the original song by Sudip Giri. The emotions, melody, and soul of the original track sparked a new creative direction, allowing this version to reflect personal experiences while honoring the essence and artistry of the original work. Much respect to Sudip Giri for the inspiration.‚Äù


‚Ñó 2026 Yabi The Goat. All rights reserved. Unauthorized use or re-upload of this content is prohibited.

About "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara"
"Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" is a popular Nepali folk song that originates from the Lamjung district of Nepal. It is a lively and upbeat song that is typically sung and danced to during festivals and social gatherings.

The lyrics of the song are in the Nepali language and describe the beauty of the Lamjung district's natural scenery, including the mountains, rivers, and forests. The song also celebrates the joy and happiness of the people living in Lamjung and their culture and traditions.

The musical arrangement of "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" typically features traditional Nepali instruments such as the madal (a type of drum), tungna (a stringed instrument), and sarangi (a bowed instrument). The song has a catchy melody and rhythm that are easy to dance along to.

Over time, "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" has become a beloved Nepali folk song that is popular across the country and is often performed by musicians and dancers at cultural events and festivals.

About "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara"
"Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" is a popular Nepali folk song that originates from the Lamjung district of Nepal. It is a lively and upbeat song that is typically sung and danced to during festivals and social gatherings.

The lyrics of the song are in the Nepali language and describe the beauty of the Lamjung district's natural scenery, including the mountains, rivers, and forests. The song also celebrates the joy and happiness of the people living in Lamjung and their culture and traditions.

The musical arrangement of "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" typically features traditional Nepali instruments such as the madal (a type of drum), tungna (a stringed instrument), and sarangi (a bowed instrument). The song has a catchy melody and rhythm that are easy to dance along to.

Over time, "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" has become a beloved Nepali folk song that is popular across the country and is often performed by musicians and dancers at cultural events and festivals.

snippet.description:
''KUBERA : the untold story'' | Full weekend Dhamaka South Movie | Hindi Movie | South ka Dhamaka

Presenting Hindi Dubbed Full Movie HD ''KUBERA : the untold story'' starring Roshan Basheer, Nisha Joseph & Abhiram Suresh. Exclusively on @AdwiseCinemaStudio

Credits:
Directed by M Radhakrishnan
Produced by  Jaison Joseph, Madhu Kalamblayil
Starring:  Roshan Basheer, Nisha Joseph, Abhiram Suresh
Music by Ganesh Raghavendra

Synopsis
Kubera Rasi revolves around a bank robbery where Abhirami plays the role of a bank employee, while Roshan Basheer play Murugans who comes from Kumbakonam to the city in search of a job. They get caught in a predicament and how they comes out of it forms the crux of the plot.

 Terikat oleh Takdir
 Dua hati. Satu pilihan. Adakah cinta akan menang, atau membalas dendam?

 Berlatarbelakangkan landskap T√ºrkiye yang menawan, *Arafta* menceritakan kisah di mana api kemarahan bertembung dengan panggilan cinta yang senyap. Apabila Ate≈ü, yang menghadapi luka masa lalunya, kembali untuk menyelesaikan akaun, semua keseimbangan berubah. Sementara itu, Mercan cuba melindungi hatinya di dunia ini yang disapu oleh takdir, berjalan di garisan halus antara kepercayaan dan syak wasangka. Rahsia tersembunyi dalam bayang-bayang, kata-kata yang tidak terucap, dan tarikan yang membara‚Ä¶ *Arafta* ialah kisah tentang ketegangan, semangat, dan perhitungan yang semakin meningkat, yang mendorong persoalan "hati atau keangkuhan?" pada setiap selekoh.

 Terikat oleh Takdir
 Dua hati. Satu pilihan. Adakah cinta atau dendam akan menang?

 Berlatarbelakangkan pemandangan Turki yang menakjubkan, Arafta menceritakan kisah di mana api kemarahan bertembung dengan panggilan cinta yang senyap. Di Arafta, dengan setiap langkah, persoalan "hati atau keangkuhan?" Ketegangan nafsu dan perhitungan yang semakin meningkat yang membuat seseorang bertanya soalan itu lagi.

BLACKHOUSEMOB presents Gimme The Loot From The album RZE (RUTHLESS ZONE)

By yourz truly RZE

This video is a music video for the song "Gimme The Loot" by RZE and Manash Ghale, produced by Shigu. The song is from RZE's album "RUTHLESS ZONE." The video features RZE and Manash Ghale performing the song, which has a hip-hop/rap style with lyrics about street life and asserting dominance (0:42-1:02, 1:31-1:53). The phrase "Give me the loot" is a prominent hook throughout the song (1:16-1:28, 2:16-2:20, 3:23-3:34). üé§ Lyrics:
Just one more tear to cry, one teardrop from my eye
You better save it for
The middle of the night when things aren't black and white
Enter, Troubadour
"Remember twenty-four?"

[Chorus]
And when I'm back in Chicago, I feel it
Another version of me, I was in it
I wave goodbye to the end of beginning

[Verse 2]
This song has started now, and you're just finding out
Now isn't that a laugh?
A major sacrifice, but clueless at the time
Enter, Caroline
"Just trust me, you'll be fine"
And when I'm back in Chicago, I feel it
Another version of me, I was in it
I wave goodbye to the end of beginning
(Goodbye, goodbye, goodbye, goodbye)

You take the man out of the city, not the city out the man
You take the man out of the city, not the city out the man
You take the man out of the city, not the city out the man
You take the man out of the‚Äî

And when I'm back in Chicago, I feel it
Another version of me, I was in it
Oh, I wave goodbye to the end of beginning
(Goodbye, goodbye)
